WEBVTT

00:00:00.518 --> 00:00:06.931
Good morning, family. How are you all doing today? I have some things on my heart.

00:00:06.932 --> 00:00:14.277
I found this prophetic word from Kent Christmas and a dream from Dana Coverstone.

00:00:14.277 --> 00:00:23.739
The Lord has really put Pastor Dana Coverstone on my heart—specifically some of the things He has shown him in these dreams.

00:00:23.740 --> 00:00:35.933
I've been going back through some of the past dreams from basically three or four years ago.

00:00:35.934 --> 00:00:45.361
I really believe he heard the Lord on many of those; some can be prayed away, and some can't.

00:00:45.362 --> 00:01:04.177
The videos I'm going to show you are very important because they go alongside what the Lord showed me about the plague that's coming and the economic collapse.

00:01:04.178 --> 00:01:10.519
Before this year is out, the death angel is being loosed upon the Earth.

00:01:10.520 --> 00:01:24.163
What they concocted and created in laboratories called Coronavirus will pale in comparison, saith the Lord, to the spirit that the death angel will loose upon the nations.

00:01:24.164 --> 00:01:37.762
It will not touch My people. For the first virus, the enemy brought it against the innocent and the old, but this, saith God, will not touch the church.

00:01:37.763 --> 00:01:49.523
Some will fall on your right hand, as I declared in Psalm 91, and they will fall on your left hand, but it shall not come nigh unto thy dwelling.

00:01:49.524 --> 00:02:31.236
What you just saw was him saying a thousand shall fall at your side and ten thousand at your right hand.

00:02:31.237 --> 00:02:44.053
If you remember what I said, it goes alongside what the Lord showed me about a glow of honey around the believers.

00:02:44.054 --> 00:03:00.619
We would go in and lay hands on people in cots. I saw cots full of bodies and people dying of this virus; it was very tragic.

00:03:00.620 --> 00:03:05.726
I've told everyone about what the Lord showed me, so I won't go over it all again.

00:03:05.727 --> 00:03:19.728
I'm just showing you that there are prophetic voices hearing that another plague and pestilence are coming.

00:03:19.729 --> 00:03:27.737
The Lord was also talking to me about getting in shape. I've been lifting weights, trying to bulk up and take care of my body more.

00:03:27.738 --> 00:03:43.883
It's been a challenge balancing eating with working out, but I'm learning a lot on YouTube.

00:03:43.884 --> 00:03:58.248
My family were not people who worked out, so this is all new. This is Bonnie Jones, Bob Jones's widow.

00:03:58.249 --> 00:04:10.161
I believe she hears the Lord, and she got a prophetic visitation about a week ago.

00:04:10.162 --> 00:04:17.758
This is a fresh video where the Lord gave her a very stern prophetic warning.

00:04:17.759 --> 00:04:33.439
She heard, 'Beware the dragon,'followed by 'biological warfare.'She associated the dragon with China.

00:04:33.440 --> 00:05:00.813
Biological warfare is the deliberate use of disease-causing agents like bacteria or toxins to kill or incapacitate as an act of war.

00:05:00.814 --> 00:05:26.061
I believe China is cooking up another virus that will be more deadly. Remember when I told you I saw the dragon?

00:05:26.062 --> 00:05:43.159
In my World War II video, I said the dragon was hiding behind a black rock, waiting for a new season. The dragon represented the COVID.

00:05:43.160 --> 00:05:57.470
I was shown in the spirit that they were taking a biological agent in a lab to release on the people, starting in Europe.

00:05:57.471 --> 00:06:12.082
I warned about that in a video called 'The Dream That I Had.'Back in April, the Lord told me He was sending another plague and that cataclysmic things would happen.

00:06:12.082 --> 00:06:17.533
He said a line of demarcation has been drawn. Calamity is coming because of disobedience to His word.

00:06:17.534 --> 00:07:14.429
Famine is imminent—not just of food, but of the Word. There has been a chokehold in America, and now He is going to release it.

00:07:14.430 --> 00:07:57.733
I'm not 100% sure what He means by a famine of food, but catastrophes like earthquakes, floods, and fires will affect our food chain.

00:07:57.734 --> 00:08:27.063
In a vision, I saw John Deere tractors sitting idle with no crops planted from the West Coast to the East Coast. There was an extreme drought.

00:08:27.064 --> 00:09:11.908
The Lord said three times, 'There's no water.'I saw the Lubbock area, Texas, and through Mexico where it was extremely dry.

00:09:11.909 --> 00:09:25.072
We need to be wise, not fearful. We cannot stop judgment, but we can lessen it through prayer.

00:09:25.073 --> 00:09:40.893
Jesus told me face-to-face that this major shaking will take place for a humbling and an awakening.

00:09:40.894 --> 00:10:14.220
We will be a sheep nation because of the prayers of our founding fathers.

00:10:14.221 --> 00:11:00.934
I've seen bridges and earthquakes preventing trucks from crossing, and I've seen gas shortages.

00:11:00.935 --> 00:11:55.155
Pastor Dana also had a dream about an 'Economic Desert.'He was at the bottom of an ocean, 2,000 feet below sea level.

00:11:55.156 --> 00:11:56.687
He saw a billboard that said 'Economic Desert.'He saw life acting normal, then suddenly changing.

00:11:56.688 --> 00:13:52.486
Cars were parked, trash was everywhere, and people were carrying brown paper grocery bags.

00:13:52.487 --> 00:15:28.853
Eventually, they had no bags, and ATMs were empty. At a checkout line, the scanner wasn't working, and a man with an empty wallet began to cry.

00:15:28.854 --> 00:15:52.005
I'm encouraging you to build the kingdom of God and ask Him what you need to do.

00:15:52.006 --> 00:16:19.002
Have some cash and resources set aside. It doesn't have to be a lot, but we are headed for hard times.

00:16:19.003 --> 00:16:29.968
I believe in miracles, but Christians will face hard things.

00:16:29.969 --> 00:17:02.706
It's not an easy-peasy life. Dana also had a dream about Wall Street and bartering.

00:17:02.707 --> 00:20:52.102
He saw people trading chickens and tools. One man traded shotgun shells for chickens; a lady traded hammers for screws.

00:20:52.103 --> 00:22:09.253
Someone traded a Rolex for horses. There were no vehicles, only bikes and skateboards.

00:22:09.254 --> 00:23:24.334
In the dream, tables were bowing under the weight of goods like unwashed eggs and rusty hand tools.

00:23:24.335 --> 00:24:19.322
I saw wooden awls and hand drills, but no power tools. The man with the shotgun shells was barefoot and used his shirt as a bag.

00:24:19.323 --> 00:25:32.031
A man representing Jesus was there and said, 'You are not as prepared as you need to be. Hearken to My word.

00:25:32.032 --> 00:26:06.379
Embrace, don't barter with My word, as you will come up short.'This situation might last longer than you think.

00:26:06.380 --> 00:27:24.576
I saw four oak trees representing four years. People were not ready for the first year, and by the end, they were bartering for ammo.

00:27:24.577 --> 00:28:26.405
If you live in a major city, think about what it would be like if you didn't have bread for your children.

00:28:26.406 --> 00:29:24.535
Pastor Dana is an elderly man, probably in his late 50s. I feel an urgency to warn you.

00:29:24.536 --> 00:30:05.636
I've seen great darkness over 2025, but also a financial outpouring for the body of Christ to provide.

00:30:05.637 --> 00:30:43.109
Mega-churches may close and move to home churches. Ask the Lord what you need for your house.

00:30:43.110 --> 00:30:46.309
Maybe it's Ramen noodles or a week's worth of food. Even FEMA says to have three days of water.

00:30:46.310 --> 00:32:13.480
Don't operate out of fear, but be alert. Every time I look for the prayers of the saints to change the direction.

00:32:13.481 --> 00:37:38.745
In 2015, the Lord gave more time, but this time He says it will manifest.

00:37:38.746 --> 00:38:57.170
I hope this video brings your attention to these things. It's smart to have candles and a source of heat for the winter.

00:38:57.171 --> 00:39:01.057
Jesus is coming back. Father, I thank You for everyone here.

00:39:01.058 --> 00:42:39.536
You always provided for me, even if it was just a piece of bologna.

00:42:39.537 --> 00:43:35.117
We command fear to bow its knee. You are El Elyon, the Most High, and Jehovah Jireh.

00:43:35.118 --> 00:43:36.073
We believe for a hundredfold return and supernatural multiplication.

00:43:36.074 --> 00:46:48.117
We speak to the seeds and the harvest. We believe for acceleration, signs, and wonders. Peace be with you. Shalom.

